A branch of the Redeemed Christian Church of God (RCCG) located around the Total Alapere area of Lagos State has been gutted by fire.  A trending video of the tragedy is doing the round in the social media. A voice-over of innocent watchers expressing pains over the fire incident confirmed the Redeemed Christian Church of God as the casualty. The video of the incident was posted on the internet by a Naija News correspondent. There were many cars on the premises of the compound in which the massive burning building of the church is located as captured in the video. The fire was on as of the time the video was uploaded without any indication of first respondersâ€™ effort to put it out. Bright fire was emitting huge smokes into the air. As of the time of filing this report, the real cause of the fire had yet to be ascertained. Video  